<sect1 id="preferences">
<title>Preferences</title>
<para>The Preferences Dialog is opened from the<guimenuitem> Menu Bar</guimenuitem> on the Main Window.</para>
<informalexample>
<para>
Settings => Preferences
</para>
</informalexample>
<para>Open the Preference Dialog to access all configuration items for &app; 
</para>
<para>The Dialog initially presents you with clickable buttons in the left hand column. Select the area you wish to work on and a graphical  menu will open. Choose the area you need to configure  and the appropriate interface will open in the larger work area .</para>
<para>The first item needed to be set up is : <link linkend="general-accounts">Accounts</link></para>
